OL,3,CIndependent traders urge Chancellor to
OL,4,Cslash business VAT in bid to survive
OL,6,FIndependent traders on Bristol's
OL,7,FGloucester Road have called on
OL,8,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt to slash
OL,9,Fbusiness VAT in the Spring Budget
OL,10,Ftomorrow, Wednesday 6 March.
OL,12,FThe financial health of the country
OL,13,Fwill be revealed in the House of
OL,14,FCommons tomorrow (March 6) with the
OL,15,Fgovernment under pressure to ease the
OL,16,Fcost of living crisis.
