OL,3,CIndependent traders urge Chancellor to
OL,4,Cslash business VAT in bid to survive
OL,6,FThose who spoke to ITV News West
OL,7,FCountry on Gloucester Road, often
OL,8,Fdubbed Europe's longest independent
OL,9,Fhigh street, doubt the Budget's
OL,10,Fcontents will stand the test of time.
OL,12,FAlice Coombs, manager of Hobbs House
OL,13,FBakery, said: "A cut in business VAT
OL,14,Fwould be really helpful.
OL,16,F"It really helped when it was taken
OL,17,Faway during Covid and with the
OL,18,Fincrease in prices of all the
OL,19,Fingredients that go into making our
OL,20,Fproducts, that 20% reduction would
OL,21,Freally help.
