OL,6,F"Gas prices are going up for us just
OL,7,Flike everyone else, too, so anything
OL,8,Fto ease costs would make a big
OL,9,Fdifference."
OL,11,FA boost for small businesses was the
OL,12,Foverriding theme at El Colmado, a
OL,13,FSpanish deli on Gloucester Road, as
OL,14,Fwell with reduced business rates top
OL,15,Fof the agenda.
