OL,3,CIndependent traders urge Chancellor to
OL,4,Cslash business VAT in bid to survive
OL,6,FShop assistant George Nichols said:
OL,7,F"If there was any way to help us
OL,8,Findependents, that would be very
OL,9,Fwelcome. We've seen increases in costs
OL,10,Fso anything to mitigate that would be
OL,11,Fuseful."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, shoppers think the
OL,14,Fgovernment might promise a lot, but
OL,15,Fdeliver less in reality.
OL,17,F"It's not going to make up for
OL,18,Feverything they're done in 12 or 13
OL,19,Fyears," said one.
